{"parentUuid":"5bc05192-c406-4a1f-803d-d6c1f287a772","isSidechain":false,"message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-7","id":"msg_01WyEWeMrCTCzp7MKsuA44A4","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01Db4oV6xgFqsarXCCDGwkuP","name":"Bash","input":{"command":"git push -u origin feat/swift-testing-migration 2>&1 | tail -2 && gh pr create --repo scottdensmore/MovieSwiftUI --base main --head feat/swift-testing-migration --title \"test: migrate XCTest unit suites to Swift Testing\" --body \"$(cat <<'EOF'\n## Summary\nFinishes the XCTest → **Swift Testing** migration (item 6 of 6 in the modernization audit). Converts all **26 unit-test suites** across the Backend, MovieSwiftFluxCore, and app targets to `@Test`/`@Suite`/`#expect`, joining the few suites already on Swift Testing. The **4 XCUITest suites stay on XCTest** — Swift Testing can't drive `XCUIApplication`.\n\nMapping applied throughout: `XCTAssert*` → `#expect`, `XCTUnwrap` → `try #require`, `XCTFail` → `Issue.record`, `XCTAssertThrowsError` → `do`/`catch` + `Issue.record`, `XCTSkipUnless` → early `return`.\n\nKey concurrency decisions (Swift Testing runs tests **in parallel** by default, unlike XCTest):\n- Pure / in-memory suites → `@Suite struct` (parallel-safe).\n- Suites touching main-actor app code → `@Suite @MainActor struct`.\n- Suites mutating shared global/file state (`AppUserDefaults`, `APIService.shared`, crash-report / iCloud-backup file I/O) → `@Suite(.serialized) final class` with `init`/`deinit` for per-test setup/teardown.\n- The completion-handler/`XCTestExpectation` flows (`APIServiceTests`, `MoviesActionsTests`, `PeopleActionsTests`) are rewritten as `async` continuation bridges — a lock-guarded collector plus an `@unchecked Sendable` box to carry the non-Sendable `Result`/`[Action]` across the continuation — so assertions run in the test's async context.\n\n## Test plan\n- [x] `swift test` — Backend (40) and MovieSwiftFluxCore (100) pass; zero XCTest references remain in those targets.\n- [x] iOS / macOS / tvOS test targets build clean under Swift 6.\n- [x] iOS unit tests (`MovieSwiftTests`) — 370 tests in 16 suites pass (parallel, no races).\n- [ ] CI: full matrix (package-tests, ios-tests, ios-tests-ipad, mac-tests, tvos-tests).\n\n🤖 Generated with [Claude Code](https://claude.com/claude-code)\nEOF\n)\" 2>&1 | tail -3","description":"Push branch and create PR for Swift Testing migration"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":2,"cache_creation_input_tokens":695,"cache_read_input_tokens":835818,"output_tokens":1036,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":695,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[{"input_tokens":2,"output_tokens":1036,"cache_read_input_tokens":835818,"cache_creation_input_tokens":695,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":695},"type":"message"}],"speed":"standard"},"diagnostics":null},"requestId":"req_011CbSF5uVDP8k9oHGRR3DrH","attributionMcpServer":"ccd_session","attributionMcpTool":"mark_chapter","type":"assistant","uuid":"d868aac9-0e1c-46e8-bb20-e089d1caff4e","timestamp":"2026-05-27T01:57:20.851Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"claude-desktop","cwd":"/Users/scottdensmore/Developer/scottdensmore/movieswiftui","sessionId":"2cae28a4-28e8-4bfa-9225-7682543f3664","version":"2.1.149","gitBranch":"feat/swift-testing-migration","slug":"snuggly-shimmying-pebble"}
