{"parentUuid":"5d7977da-5540-4421-ae2c-b0cb99023f43","isSidechain":false,"message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-7","id":"msg_01X4UbgTuCQhaR1ertsjWEMy","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Modernization 6 is implemented and pushed as **PR #12** — the final item. While CI runs the full matrix, I'll wait for it to settle, then check Copilot and merge. Quick status for you:\n\n## Modernization 6 (XCTest → Swift Testing) — PR #12 open\n\n- **26 unit-test suites** converted to Swift Testing across Backend (3), FluxCore (7), and the app target (16); the **4 XCUITest suites stay on XCTest** (Swift Testing can't drive `XCUIApplication`).\n- Parallelized the bulk conversion across subagents, then build-verified and fixed their output myself — caught and corrected several real issues: nested `#require` (macro can't nest), a deprecated `#expect{}throws:{}` form (→ `do`/`catch`), `return Issue.record(...)` in a `Void` context, a key-path predicate confusing `#require`'s throws-inference, and a missing `import SwiftUIFlux`.\n- Handled the tricky async suites myself: the completion-handler/`XCTestExpectation` flows (`APIServiceTests`, `MoviesActionsTests`, `PeopleActionsTests`) now bridge to `async` via `withCheckedContinuation` + a lock-guarded collector and `@unchecked Sendable` boxes.\n- Concurrency-aware suite choices for Swift Testing's default parallelism: `@Suite struct` (pure), `@Suite @MainActor struct` (main-actor code), `@Suite(.serialized) final class` (shared global/file state, with `init`/`deinit`).\n- **Local verification (all green):** Backend (40) + FluxCore (100) pass via `swift test`; iOS/macOS/tvOS test targets build clean; **370 iOS unit tests pass in 16 Swift Testing suites** (parallel, no races).\n\nI'll address any Copilot review, resolve threads, and merge once CI is green — then all six modernization items will be complete."}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":2,"cache_creation_input_tokens":491,"cache_read_input_tokens":837653,"output_tokens":661,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":491,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[{"input_tokens":2,"output_tokens":661,"cache_read_input_tokens":837653,"cache_creation_input_tokens":491,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":491},"type":"message"}],"speed":"standard"},"diagnostics":null},"requestId":"req_011CbSF8mQsmh4RZaZ2YPcpW","attributionMcpServer":"ccd_session","attributionMcpTool":"mark_chapter","type":"assistant","uuid":"2a6d2cac-28eb-4949-b911-8179cb2eb4bc","timestamp":"2026-05-27T01:57:57.372Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"claude-desktop","cwd":"/Users/scottdensmore/Developer/scottdensmore/movieswiftui","sessionId":"2cae28a4-28e8-4bfa-9225-7682543f3664","version":"2.1.149","gitBranch":"feat/swift-testing-migration","slug":"snuggly-shimmying-pebble"}
