{"parentUuid":"a786f208-b25c-4002-a828-3964d659f188","isSidechain":false,"message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-7","id":"msg_01WxMPJtWCnExBrrtd4wDyiL","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Audit refresh done. The codebase is already quite modern after the six items — most legacy patterns are gone (`NavigationView` 0, `.accentColor` 0, `.navigationBarItems` 0, `UIScreen.main` 0, `if #available` 0). A few genuine things remain:\n\n## Findings\n\n**1. `.cornerRadius(_:)` — 14 sites across 10 files** (app + UI package)\nSoft-deprecated in iOS 17. The modern replacement is `.clipShape(.rect(cornerRadius:))`. Clean, mechanical sweep — same shape as the `.foregroundColor` → `.foregroundStyle` one.\n\n**2. Two dead `@available` version gates**\nDeployment minimum is now iOS/macOS/tvOS **26**, so these are always-true dead code:\n- `MetricKitCrashReporter`: `@available(iOS 14.0, macOS 12.0, *)`\n- `SearchField`: `@available(iOS 13.0, OSX 10.15, *)`\n\n(The `@available(tvOS, unavailable)` / `watchOS, unavailable` gates on `SearchField` are *intentional* platform exclusions and stay.)\n\n**3. Combine → async/await for image loading** *(larger, optional)*\n`ImageService.fetchImage` still returns an `AnyPublisher` (Combine `dataTaskPublisher`), and `ImageLoader` is an `ObservableObject` (`@Published image` + a Combine `cancellable`). These could move to `async/await` + `@Observable`. It's more invasive (image loading is used app-wide) and higher-risk than 1 & 2.\n\n**Not actionable:** the remaining `ObservableObject`/`@EnvironmentObject`/`@StateObject`/`@ObservedObject` are all tied to the pinned SwiftUIFlux `Store` — can't migrate those without forking the dependency. (`NavigationLink(isActive:)` and a flagged `.animation` were false positives — the animation is already the modern `.animation(_:value:)` form.)"}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":2,"cache_creation_input_tokens":3114,"cache_read_input_tokens":861256,"output_tokens":2172,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":3114,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[{"input_tokens":2,"output_tokens":2172,"cache_read_input_tokens":861256,"cache_creation_input_tokens":3114,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":3114},"type":"message"}],"speed":"standard"},"diagnostics":null},"requestId":"req_011CbSLD935NFNoS6ESX9Jd9","type":"assistant","uuid":"7c5c91dc-28b2-4343-adaa-012947cedc9b","timestamp":"2026-05-27T03:04:44.126Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"claude-desktop","cwd":"/Users/scottdensmore/Developer/scottdensmore/movieswiftui","sessionId":"2cae28a4-28e8-4bfa-9225-7682543f3664","version":"2.1.149","gitBranch":"main","slug":"snuggly-shimmying-pebble"}
