{"parentUuid":"04a8a357-22ff-4042-9e73-01027c8fc545","isSidechain":false,"attachment":{"type":"task_reminder","content":[{"id":"1","subject":"Modernization 1: ContentUnavailableView for empty/error states","description":"Replace hand-built empty/error-state VStacks with ContentUnavailableView (iOS 17+) across search no-results, Fan Club error, empty wishlist/seenlist, no-people, etc. Branch → test → PR → merge.","activeForm":"Adopting ContentUnavailableView","status":"completed","blocks":[],"blockedBy":[]},{"id":"2","subject":"Modernization 2: @Observable for app-owned stores","description":"Migrate the 2 clean view-observed app stores to @Observable: MoviesSelectedMenuStore (1 consumer: MoviesHome) + IntentNavigationStore (2 consumers: HomeView/TabbarView, SplitView). Deferred: SearchTextObservable (open + 3 subclasses + Combine debounce + SearchField API), ImageLoader (hot path, Backend pkg, many consumers), MovieSpotlightIndexer (not view-observed).","activeForm":"Migrating stores to @Observable","status":"completed","blocks":[],"blockedBy":[]},{"id":"3","subject":"Modernization 3: async/await networking in APIService","description":"Convert APIService's completion-handler dataTask networking to URLSession async/await (data(for:)) behind the existing AsyncAction/dispatch facade.","activeForm":"Modernizing APIService to async/await","status":"completed","blocks":[],"blockedBy":[]},{"id":"4","subject":"Modernization 4: .foregroundColor → .foregroundStyle","description":"Mechanically replace .foregroundColor( with .foregroundStyle( across ~174 sites (soft-deprecated API). Low risk, future-proofing.","activeForm":"Migrating foregroundColor to foregroundStyle","status":"completed","blocks":[],"blockedBy":[]},{"id":"5","subject":"Modernization 5: Swift 6 language mode + strict concurrency","description":"Move from swiftLanguageModes .v5 to Swift 6 language mode + strict concurrency: Sendable conformance, @MainActor isolation, data-race safety across app + packages. Big