{"parentUuid":"dbbd64d9-b0bc-494b-95e4-382877baa99b","isSidechain":false,"message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-7","id":"msg_01VSc7D8Cqjvw73GdS2f9uXi","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"All CI checks pass. Copilot's one comment is a fair correction: my PR description overstated — `SearchTextObservable` (UI package) still uses `ObservableObject`/`@Published`/Combine (its debounce pipeline), so this PR doesn't remove *all* remaining Combine usage. The code is fine; I'll correct the description, reply, and resolve. Let me update the PR body:"}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":2,"cache_creation_input_tokens":783,"cache_read_input_tokens":922954,"output_tokens":2202,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":783,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[{"input_tokens":2,"output_tokens":2202,"cache_read_input_tokens":922954,"cache_creation_input_tokens":783,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":783},"type":"message"}],"speed":"standard"},"diagnostics":null},"requestId":"req_011CbSUTo3eQS23mpTwJjGTy","type":"assistant","uuid":"d257f304-1215-4bab-98c2-b166afce5a2c","timestamp":"2026-05-27T04:52:52.333Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"claude-desktop","cwd":"/Users/scottdensmore/Developer/scottdensmore/movieswiftui","sessionId":"2cae28a4-28e8-4bfa-9225-7682543f3664","version":"2.1.149","gitBranch":"feat/async-image-loading","slug":"snuggly-shimmying-pebble"}
{"parentUuid":"d257f304-1215-4bab-98c2-b166afce5a2c","isSidechain":false,"message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-7","id":"msg_01VSc7D8Cqjvw73GdS2f9uXi","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01Bj7K4rFvA2aysuFJLFTv6p","name":"Bash","input":{"command":"gh pr edit 14 --repo scottdensmore/MovieSwiftUI --body \"$(cat <<'EOF'\n## Summary\nModernizes the app's image loading from Combine to structured concurrency + the Observation framework.\n\n- **`ImageService.fetchImage`**: `AnyPublisher<Data?, Never>` (Combine `dataTaskPublisher`) → `async -> Data?` over `URLSession.data(from:)`, returning `nil` on transport error (same contract as the old `.catch { Just(nil) }`). Combine/SwiftUI imports dropped.\n- **`ImageLoader`**: `ObservableObject` + `@Published image` + a Combine `AnyCancellable` → a `@MainActor @Observable` class that loads via an unstructured `Task` (download off-main, publish `image` on the main actor; task cancelled in `deinit`). `ImageLoaderCache` is now `@MainActor`.\n- **`ImageService.Size`** conforms to `Sendable` (trivial raw-value enum) so it can cross into the loading `Task`.\n- **Consumers** (~12 image views): `@ObservedObject var imageLoader` → plain `var` (an `@Observable` object is observed by reading it in `body`); `CarouselImageView`'s `@StateObject` → `@State`.\n\nScope note: this is the image-loading path only. `SearchTextObservable` (UI package) intentionally **stays** on `ObservableObject`/`@Published` + a Combine `debounce` pipeline — debounce is a natural Combine fit and the type is `open` and subclassed by app view models, so converting it is a separate, larger change. The remaining `ObservableObject`/`@EnvironmentObject` usage on the `Store` is bound to the pinned SwiftUIFlux dependency.\n\n## Test plan\nBehavior-preserving refactor (image loading semantics unchanged; the network path wasn't unit-tested before or after).\n- [x] `swift test` — Backend: 40 tests pass (including the cache-identity `ImageLoaderCacheTests`); 0 warnings.\n- [x] iOS / macOS / tvOS app targets build clean, 0 warnings.\n- [x] CI: full matrix green.\n\n🤖 Generated with [Claude Code](https://claude.com/claude-code)\nEOF\n)\" 2>&1 | tail -1","description":"Correct PR #14 description re SearchTextObservable"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":2,"cache_creation_input_tokens":783,"cache_read_input_tokens":922954,"output_tokens":2202,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":783,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[{"input_tokens":2,"output_tokens":2202,"cache_read_input_tokens":922954,"cache_creation_input_tokens":783,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":783},"type":"message"}],"speed":"standard"},"diagnostics":null},"requestId":"req_011CbSUTo3eQS23mpTwJjGTy","type":"assistant","uuid":"3e5324a7-a086-4867-9c58-eb1aa488aef9","timestamp":"2026-05-27T04:53:01.042Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"claude-desktop","cwd":"/Users/scottdensmore/Developer/scottdensmore/movieswiftui","sessionId":"2cae28a4-28e8-4bfa-9225-7682543f3664","version":"2.1.149","gitBranch":"feat/async-image-loading","slug":"snuggly-shimmying-pebble"}
