{"parentUuid":"b2db61cf-e646-427b-855f-3c819004c96d","isSidechain":false,"message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-7","id":"msg_01B1ej9TSpRDbRMxLAnf1wBg","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"","signature":""}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1290,"cache_read_input_tokens":962730,"output_tokens":1724,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1290,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[{"input_tokens":1,"output_tokens":1724,"cache_read_input_tokens":962730,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1290,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1290},"type":"message"}],"speed":"standard"},"diagnostics":null},"requestId":"req_011CbXx1HyUAmWy8pd3qPPHx","type":"assistant","uuid":"ec44e7c8-2e00-4ab1-bbc2-acc829ee5879","timestamp":"2026-05-30T02:16:59.421Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"claude-desktop","cwd":"/Users/scottdensmore/Developer/scottdensmore/movieswiftui","sessionId":"2cae28a4-28e8-4bfa-9225-7682543f3664","version":"2.1.149","gitBranch":"main","slug":"snuggly-shimmying-pebble"}
{"parentUuid":"ec44e7c8-2e00-4ab1-bbc2-acc829ee5879","isSidechain":false,"message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-7","id":"msg_01B1ej9TSpRDbRMxLAnf1wBg","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Verified — all 6 `print()` calls in non-test source are properly inside `#if DEBUG`. (My earlier check just had too short a lookback window.)\n\n## Audit refresh #2 — codebase is clean\n\n| Pattern | Count | Notes |\n|---|---|---|\n| `.alert(isPresented:)` / `.actionSheet` | 0 | — |\n| `.navigationBarLeading`/`Trailing`/`Hidden` | 0 | — |\n| `.navigationBarBackButtonHidden` / `.pickerStyle(.wheel)` | 0 | — |\n| `.navigationBarTitle(\"string\")` | 0 | (the 6 matches are `.navigationBarTitleDisplayMode(_:)` — current API) |\n| `.onChange(of:)` deprecated 1-arg form | 0 | (all 30 explicit closures use the iOS-17 `{ _, newValue in }` 2-arg form; the other 2 are 0-arg) |\n| `try!` / `as!` / `fatalError(` / implicit-unwrap properties | 0 | — |\n| `TODO` / `FIXME` / `HACK` | 0 | — |\n| `if let x = x` / `guard let x = x` shorthand opportunities | 0 | (already using the modern `if let x` shorthand) |\n| `Bundle.main` on localized strings | 0 | (packages correctly use `bundle: .module`) |\n| `print()` leakage outside `#if DEBUG` | 0 | (all 6 prints in non-test source are properly gated) |\n\n**Not modernization, just style observations** (no PR warranted):\n- 7 `DispatchQueue.main.async`/`asyncAfter(deadline:)` calls in app views — almost all are `asyncAfter` for short UI animation delays. That's the idiomatic API for delayed work; converting to `Task { try? await Task.sleep(...) }` is a style preference, not a deprecation.\n- `SettingsForm.swift` (1,472 LOC) and `MovieDetail.swift` (1,292 LOC) are the biggest files — both well-organized SwiftUI roots. Splitting into more subviews is refactoring/architecture, not modernization.\n\nThe codebase is now genuinely at the floor — every actionable item from both audits is shipped (8 PRs merged this session). The only remaining \"non-modern\" pieces are the two well-understood intentional holdouts: `SearchTextObservable`'s Combine debounce (would just reimplement debounce with `Task.sleep` for no clear gain) and the SwiftUIFlux `Store`'s `ObservableObject`/`@EnvironmentObject` usage (pinned external dep).\n\nI'd say leave it here. If you'd like, I can spin off any of the style observations as a low-priority chore, but they're not modernization in any real sense."}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1290,"cache_read_input_tokens":962730,"output_tokens":1724,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1290,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[{"input_tokens":1,"output_tokens":1724,"cache_read_input_tokens":962730,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1290,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1290},"type":"message"}],"speed":"standard"},"diagnostics":null},"requestId":"req_011CbXx1HyUAmWy8pd3qPPHx","type":"assistant","uuid":"3a269e72-e947-415d-ab00-4ac3d4515d21","timestamp":"2026-05-30T02:17:11.298Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"claude-desktop","cwd":"/Users/scottdensmore/Developer/scottdensmore/movieswiftui","sessionId":"2cae28a4-28e8-4bfa-9225-7682543f3664","version":"2.1.149","gitBranch":"main","slug":"snuggly-shimmying-pebble"}
