{"parentUuid":"fee4ee96-0467-48e4-9132-3b07ad2153e3","isSidechain":false,"message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-7","id":"msg_016rWrqy3pKxr1TSh3ksWKkH","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Here's what the test-modernity audit turned up:\n\n**Swift Testing suites — already modern, but unused advanced features:**\n- 0 `@Test(arguments:)` parameterized tests\n- 0 `.tags`, 0 `withKnownIssue`, 0 `confirmation(...)`\n- All suites use modern `@Suite` / `@Test` / `#expect` / `#require` correctly\n- Async bridging uses custom `withCheckedContinuation` + `@unchecked Sendable` boxes (could use `confirmation` in some cases, but the current pattern is fine for capturing dispatched actions)\n\n**Parameterizable candidate groups (would benefit from `@Test(arguments:)`):**\n- `APIServiceTests`: HTTP status 401/500 pair\n- `ReducerTests`: 12 tests in PageOne/PageTwo pairs across 6 reducers\n- `PeopleActionsTests`: 5 success/`DoesNotDispatchOnFailure` pairs (FetchDetail, FetchImages, FetchPeopleCredits, FetchMovieCasts, FetchSearch)\n- `AppDataICloudBackupTests`: 11 round-trip-shaped tests\n\n**XCUITest files (must stay XCTest — Swift Testing can't drive XCUIApplication):**\n- `MovieSwiftUITests.swift`: 59 methods, 10 use old `waitForExpectations` / `expectation(description:)`, 0 use `await fulfillment(of:)`\n- `MovieSwiftMacUITests.swift`: 38 methods, 8 use old `waitForExpectations`\n- `MovieSwiftTVUITests.swift`: 15 methods, 0 old-wait usage (already clean)\n\nThese XCUITest waits could be modernized to `func testX() async throws` + `await fulfillment(of:expectations, timeout:)` — current XCTest API, less verbose, no completion-handler indirection."}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":6,"cache_creation_input_tokens":13691,"cache_read_input_tokens":15501,"output_tokens":1182,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_inp