{"parentUuid":"fa806132-344d-4b5e-b32d-60c9d64730ee","isSidechain":false,"promptId":"af759ad8-76cc-4b58-b2d3-322690ab2306","type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01GRyLJ6AJRWCTRie2SxGSdA","type":"tool_result","content":"1215\t    /// end, on a real iOS simulator.\n1216\t    func testSettingsRegionPickerSaveDispatchesAndDismisses() {\n1217\t        // Pin the persisted region to \"US\" via NSUserDefaults launch-arg\n1218\t        // override (`-key value`). Without this, a previous run of this\n1219\t        // test would have left `user_region = AL` in the simulator's\n1220\t        // persistent defaults, so the next run would start with Albania\n1221\t        // already selected — and the \"scroll the popover up to find\n1222\t        // Albania\" loop below would be wrong (we'd already be on it).\n1223\t        //\n1224\t        // The launch-arg override shadows persisted defaults for this\n1225\t        // launch only; the savePreferences write inside the test still\n1226\t        // mutates the persistent defaults to AL, but the next run's\n1227\t        // launch arg overrides that again. Test is now idempotent\n1228\t        // regardless of what state previous runs left behind.\n1229\t        let app = launchApp(additionalLaunchArguments: [\"-user_region\", \"US\"])"}]},"uuid":"a73fea08-dda7-4af5-a1ce-f26f50ff2bdf","timestamp":"2026-05-30T02:25:59.272Z","toolUseResult":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/Users/scottdensmore/Developer/scottdensmore/movieswiftui/MovieSwift/MovieSwiftUITests/MovieSwiftUITests.swift","content":"    /// end, on a real iOS simulator.\n    func testSettingsRegionPickerSaveDispatchesAndDismisses() {\n        // Pin the persisted region to \"US\" via NSUserDefaults launch-arg\n        // override (`-key value`). Without this, a previous run of this\n        // test would have left `user_region = AL` in the simulator's\n        // persistent defaults, so the next run would start with Albania\n        // already selected — and the \"scroll the popover up to find\n        // Albania\" loop below would be wrong (we'd already be on it).\n        //\n        // The launch-arg override shadows persisted defaults for this\n        // launch only; the savePreferences write inside the test still\n        // mutates the persistent defaults to AL, but the next run's\n        // launch arg overrides that again. Test is now idempotent\n        // regardless of what state previous runs left behind.\n        let app = launchApp(additionalLaunchArguments: [\"-user_region\", \"US\"])","numLines":15,"startLine":1215,"totalLines":1544}},"sourceToolAssistantUUID":"fa806132-344d-4b5e-b32d-60c9d64730ee","userType":"external","entrypoint":"claude-desktop","cwd":"/Users/scottdensmore/Developer/scottdensmore/movieswiftui","sessionId":"2cae28a4-28e8-4bfa-9225-7682543f3664","version":"2.1.149","gitBranch":"modernize/xcuitest-async-fulfillment","slug":"snuggly-shimmying-pebble"}
