{"parentUuid":"fffa28ab-681e-4dbe-a7a2-a322b2f195f3","isSidechain":false,"attachment":{"type":"task_reminder","content":[{"id":"1","subject":"Modernization 1: ContentUnavailableView for empty/error states","description":"Replace hand-built empty/error-state VStacks with ContentUnavailableView (iOS 17+) across search no-results, Fan Club error, empty wishlist/seenlist, no-people, etc. Branch → test → PR → merge.","activeForm":"Adopting ContentUnavailableView","status":"completed","blocks":[],"blockedBy":[]},{"id":"2","subject":"Modernization 2: @Observable for app-owned stores","description":"Migrate the 2 clean view-observed app stores to @Observable: MoviesSelectedMenuStore (1 consumer: MoviesHome) + IntentNavigationStore (2 consumers: HomeView/TabbarView, SplitView). Deferred: SearchTextObservable (open + 3 subclasses + Combine debounce + SearchField API), ImageLoader (hot path, Backend pkg, many consumers), MovieSpotlightIndexer (not view-observed).","activeForm":"Migrating stores to @Observable","status":"completed","blocks":[],"blockedBy":[]},{"id":"3","subject":"Modernization 3: async/await networking in APIService","description":"Convert APIService's completion-handler dataTask networking to URLSession async/await (data(for:)) behind the existing AsyncAction/dispatch facade.","activeForm":"Modernizing APIService to async/await","status":"completed","blocks":[],"blockedBy":[]},{"id":"4","subject":"Modernization 4: .foregroundColor → .foregroundStyle","description":"Mechanically replace .foregroundColor( with .foregroundStyle( across ~174 sites (soft-deprecated API). Low risk, future-proofing.","activeForm":"Migrating foregroundColor to foregroundStyle","status":"completed","blocks":[],"blockedBy":[]},{"id":"5","subject":"Modernization 5: Swift 6 language mode + strict concurrency","description":"Move from swiftLanguageModes .v5 to Swift 6 language mode + strict concurrency: Sendable conformance, @MainActor isolation, data-race safety across app + packages. Big effort; assess SwiftUIFlux dep compatibility.","activeForm":"Adopting Swift 6 strict concurrency","status":"completed","blocks":[],"blockedBy":[]},{"id":"6","subject":"Modernization 6: finish XCTest → Swift Testing migration","description":"Continue migrating XCTest (29 XCTestCase) to Swift Testing (@Test/#expect); 7 already migrated. Mechanical.","activeForm":"Migrating tests to Swift Testing","status":"completed","blocks":[],"blockedBy":[]},{"id":"7","subject":"Audit fix A: .cornerRadius → clipShape + dead @available cleanup","description":"Replace 14 deprecated .cornerRadius(_:) with .clipShape(RoundedRectangle(cornerRadius:)) across app+UI package; remove 2 always-true @available version gates (MetricKit iOS14/macOS12, SearchField iOS13/macOS10.15) keeping tvOS/watchOS unavailable gates. Build iOS/macOS/tvOS, PR, merge.","status":"completed","blocks":[],"blockedBy":[]},{"id":"8","subject":"Audit fix B: Combine → async/await image loading","description":"Modernize ImageService.fetchImage (AnyPublisher/dataTaskPublisher) and ImageLoader (ObservableObject/@Published + Combine cancellable) to async/await + @Observable. Verify image loading across app. Build all targets, PR, merge.","status":"completed","blocks":[],"blockedBy":[]},{"id":"9","subject":"Audit fix C: XCUITest async/await fulfillment","description":"Convert ~18 XCUITest methods in MovieSwiftUITests + MovieSwiftMacUITests from waitForExpectations to async test methods using await fulfillment(of:timeout:).","activeForm":"Modernizing XCUITest waits","status":"in_progress","blocks":[],"blockedBy":[]},{"id":"10","subject":"Audit fix D: Parameterize ReducerTests pairs","description":"Collapse 12 PageOne/PageTwo reducer tests into 6 @Test(arguments:) parameterized tests in ReducerTests.","activeForm":"Parameterizing ReducerTests","status":"pending","blocks":[],"blockedBy":[]},{"id":"11","subject":"Audit fix E: Parameterize PeopleActionsTests pairs","description":"Convert 5 success/DoesNotDispatchOnFailure pairs in PeopleActionsTests to @Test(arguments:) form.","activeForm":"Parameterizing PeopleActionsTests","status":"pending","blocks":[],"blockedBy":[]}],"itemCount":11},"type":"attachment","uuid":"42a0c457-20eb-46d2-b4af-30b67e27cafa","timestamp":"2026-05-30T02:27:10.582Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"claude-desktop","cwd":"/Users/scottdensmore/Developer/scottdensmore/movieswiftui","sessionId":"2cae28a4-28e8-4bfa-9225-7682543f3664","version":"2.1.149","gitBranch":"modernize/xcuitest-async-fulfillment","slug":"snuggly-shimmying-pebble"}
