{"parentUuid":"d30b4830-1191-4777-9acf-42cab5868b23","isSidechain":false,"message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-7","id":"msg_01U9nuoBS24rtZFUyFQDb3kY","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01DaUpXgxStSkoUD65TJ7bij","name":"Bash","input":{"command":"git -C /Users/scottdensmore/Developer/scottdensmore/movieswiftui add MovieSwift/Packages/MovieSwiftFluxCore/Tests/MovieSwiftFluxCoreTests/ReducerTests.swift && git -C /Users/scottdensmore/Developer/scottdensmore/movieswiftui commit -m \"$(cat <<'EOF'\ntest(reducers): parameterize 6 PageOne/PageTwo reducer pairs with @Test(arguments:)\n\nCollapses 12 individual pagination tests in `ReducerTests` into 6\nparameterized `@Test(arguments:)` tests:\n\n- moviesReducerSetMovieMenuListPaginates (was: SetMovieMenuList Page{One,Two})\n- moviesReducerSetSearchPaginates       (was: SetSearch Page{One,Two})\n- moviesReducerSetMovieForGenrePaginates (was: SetMovieForGenre Page{One,Two})\n- moviesReducerSetMovieWithKeywordPaginates (was: SetMovieWithKeyword Page{One,Two})\n- peopleReducerSetSearchPaginates        (was: SetSearch Page{One,Two})\n- peopleReducerSetPopularPaginates       (was: SetPopular Page{One,Two...})\n\nEach parameterized test asserts the shared shape: page 1 replaces the\nlist keyed by id/query, page > 1 appends. The SetPopular one also\nasserts loading-flag normalization for both pages (the reducer always\nsets popularLoading=false / popularInitialLoadCompleted=true on any\nsuccessful response — verified in PeopleReducer.swift; previously only\nthe page-1 test checked that).\n\nSwift Testing reports each case individually\n(\"Test X with 2 test cases passed\"), so failure attribution stays\nper-case. 44 tests total, all green locally.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.7 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>\nEOF\n)\"","description":"Commit reducer parameterization"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":3115,"cache_read_input_tokens":142422,"output_tokens":852,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":3115,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[{"input_tokens":1,"output_tokens":852,"cache_read_input_tokens":142422,"cache_creation_input_tokens":3115,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":3115},"type":"message"}],"speed":"standard"},"diagnostics":null},"requestId":"req_011CbXyh2zJDXgVicZ1nSjQj","attributionMcpServer":"ccd_session","attributionMcpTool":"mark_chapter","type":"assistant","uuid":"370830c3-4b9f-45d0-a138-c25ea8768898","timestamp":"2026-05-30T02:39:02.825Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"claude-desktop","cwd":"/Users/scottdensmore/Developer/scottdensmore/movieswiftui/MovieSwift/Packages/MovieSwiftFluxCore","sessionId":"2cae28a4-28e8-4bfa-9225-7682543f3664","version":"2.1.149","gitBranch":"modernize/parameterize-reducer-tests","slug":"snuggly-shimmying-pebble"}
