{"parentUuid":"cca1caea-d563-4482-b370-97b6e9b5dac5","isSidechain":false,"promptId":"af759ad8-76cc-4b58-b2d3-322690ab2306","type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01Srit71HEi6uvZw8AxKidwr","type":"tool_result","content":"1\t{\"parentUuid\":null,\"isSidechain\":true,\"promptId\":\"af759ad8-76cc-4b58-b2d3-322690ab2306\",\"agentId\":\"aa668c0dbd31f7b9a\",\"type\":\"user\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":\"Watch GitHub PR #15 (scottdensmore/MovieSwiftUI, branch modernize/xcuitest-async-fulfillment) until all required checks settle.\\n\\nUse the GitHub CLI (`gh`). Required checks for this repo: Analyze (actions), Analyze (ruby), Analyze (swift), CodeQL, ios-tests, ios-tests-ipad, mac-tests, package-tests, tvos-tests.\\n\\nSteps:\\n1. `gh pr checks 15 --watch --interval 30` to wait for all checks to settle.\\n2. After it settles, run `gh pr checks 15` once more to capture the final pass/fail table.\\n3. Also run `gh pr view 15 --json mergeable,mergeStateStatus -q '\\\"mergeable=\\\" + (.mergeable // \\\"null\\\") + \\\" state=\\\" + (.mergeStateStatus // \\\"null\\\")'`.\\n4. Also check for any Copilot review comments: `gh api \\\"repos/scottdensmore/MovieSwiftUI/pulls/15/comments\\\" --jq '[.[] | select(.user.login == \\\"copilot-pull-request-reviewer[bot]\\\") | {path: .path, line: .line, body: .body[0:300]}]'`.\\n\\nReport in this format under 200 words:\\n=== settled ===\\n<one line per check: name<TAB>state<TAB>elapsed<TAB>url>\\n=== mergeable ===\\nmergeable=<X> state=<Y>\\n=== Copilot ===\\n<one block per comment: [path#line] body, OR \\\"none\\\">\\n\\nIf any check fails, include the failure URL in the settled section.\"},\"uuid\":\"10105082-2ccb-4056-8e76-2f9a1baae349\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-05-30T02:34:02.816Z\",\"userType\":\"external\",\"entrypoint\":\"claude-desktop\",\"cwd\":\"/Users/scottdensmore/Developer/scottdensmore/movieswiftui/MovieSwift\",\"sessionId\":\"2cae28a4-28e8-4bfa-9225-7682543f3664\",\"version\":\"2.