text\":\"The watch command is running in the background. I'll wait for it to complete.\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"stop_details\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":6,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":19434,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"output_tokens\":25,\"server_tool_use\":{\"web_search_requests\":0,\"web_fetch_requests\":0},\"service_tier\":\"standard\",\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":19434},\"inference_geo\":\"\",\"iterations\":[{\"input_tokens\":6,\"output_tokens\":25,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":19434,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":19434,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"type\":\"message\"}],\"speed\":\"standard\"},\"diagnostics\":{\"cache_miss_reason\":{\"type\":\"tools_changed\",\"cache_missed_input_tokens\":15431}}},\"requestId\":\"REDACTED\",\"attributionAgent\":\"general-purpose\",\"type\":\"assistant\",\"uuid\":\"73fa068b-d78a-47b3-98fc-44a004695854\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-05-30T02:44:10.579Z\",\"userType\":\"external\",\"entrypoint\":\"claude-desktop\",\"cwd\":\"/Users/scottdensmore/Developer/scottdensmore/movieswiftui/MovieSwift\",\"sessionId\":\"2cae28a4-28e8-4bfa-9225-7682543f3664\",\"version\":\"2.1.149\",\"gitBranch\":\"modernize/parameterize-reducer-tests\",\"slug\":\"snuggly-shimmying-pebble\"}\n","numLines":10,"startLine":1,"totalLines":10}},"sourceToolAssistantUUID":"cca1caea-d563-4482-b370-97b6e9b5dac5","userType":"external","entrypoint":"claude-desktop","cwd":"/Users/scottdensmore/Developer/scottdensmore/movieswiftui/MovieSwift/Packages/MovieSwiftFluxCore","sessionId":"2cae28a4-28e8-4bfa-9225-7682543f3664","version":"2.1.149","gitBranch":"modernize/parameterize-reducer-tests","slug":"snuggly-shimmying-pebble"}
{"parentUuid":"3f75218b-7518-411f-be63-138ea14acc67","isSidechain":false,"message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-7","id":"msg_017W6NyxJ8yubAEYZCoHXkg7","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01UppbpwcMnS8RjwRVQA5q2K","name":"Bash","input":{"command":"gh pr create --base main --head modernize/parameterize-reducer-tests --title \"test(reducers): parameterize 6 PageOne/PageTwo pairs with @Test(arguments:)\" --body \"$(cat <<'EOF'\n## Summary\n\n- Collapses 12 individual pagination tests in `ReducerTests` into 6 `@Test(arguments:)` parameterized tests:\n  - `moviesReducerSetMovieMenuListPaginates` (was: `SetMovieMenuListPage{One,Two}*`)\n  - `moviesReducerSetSearchPaginates` (was: `SetSearchPage{One,Two}*`)\n  - `moviesReducerSetMovieForGenrePaginates` (was: `SetMovieForGenrePage{One,Two}*`)\n  - `moviesReducerSetMovieWithKeywordPaginates` (was: `SetMovieWithKeywordPage{One,Two}*`)\n  - `peopleReducerSetSearchPaginates` (was: `peopleReducerSetSearchPage{One,Two}*`)\n  - `peopleReducerSetPopularPaginates` (was: `peopleReducerSetPopularPage{One,Two}*`)\n- Each parameterized test asserts the shared pagination shape: page 1 replaces the keyed list, page > 1 appends.\n- `peopleReducerSetPopularPaginates` additionally asserts loading-flag normalization (`popularLoading=false`, `popularInitialLoadCompleted=true`) for both pages — the reducer in `PeopleReducer.swift` always sets these on a successful response regardless of page, so it was an asymmetry in coverage before.\n\n## Behavior\n\nSwift Testing reports each parameterized case individually, e.g. `Test moviesReducerSetMovieMenuListPaginates(...) with 2 test cases passed`, and surfaces argument values in any failure. So failure attribution stays per-case — no loss of debuggability compared to two split methods.\n\nNet test count: 50 → 44 tests in `ReducerTests` (6 pairs collapsed).\n\n## Test plan\n\n- [ ] `swift test --filter ReducerTests` passes locally (verified — 44 tests, 1 suite, green).\n- [ ] CI: `package-tests`, `ios-tests`, `ios-tests-ipad`, `mac-tests`, `tvos-tests`, Analyze (actions/ruby/swift), CodeQL all green.\n\n🤖 Generated with [Claude Code](https://claude.com/claude-code)\nEOF\n)\"","description":"Open reducer parameterization PR"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":798,"cache_read_input_tokens":146487,"output_tokens":1171,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":798,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[{"input_tokens":1,"output_tokens":1171,"cache_read_input_tokens":146487,"cache_creation_input_tokens":798,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":798},"type":"message"}],"speed":"standard"},"diagnostics":null},"requestId":"req_011CbXzDpZoKGCcQN5M7LPbk","attributionMcpServer":"ccd_session","attributionMcpTool":"mark_chapter","type":"assistant","uuid":"bb86c5af-910e-4c73-8802-16c86c9690b2","timestamp":"2026-05-30T02:46:01.973Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"claude-desktop","cwd":"/Users/scottdensmore/Developer/scottdensmore/movieswiftui/MovieSwift/Packages/MovieSwiftFluxCore","sessionId":"2cae28a4-28e8-4bfa-9225-7682543f3664","version":"2.1.149","gitBranch":"modernize/parameterize-reducer-tests","slug":"snuggly-shimmying-pebble"}
