{"parentUuid":"92c6ef56-dfa2-4bea-ab53-3fb151b06c75","isSidechain":false,"message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-7","id":"msg_01Wt2w9QA2j6asbW8ASYgVSc","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"All 8 tests pass (was 12 originally: 5 success + 5 failure + 2 FetchPopular = 12; now 8: 5 success + 1 parameterized failure (covering 5 cases) + 2 FetchPopular). Let me commit, push, and PR:"}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":2174,"cache_read_input_tokens":196800,"output_tokens":872,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":2174,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[{"input_tokens":1,"output_tokens":872,"cache_read_input_tokens":196800,"cache_creation_input_tokens":2174,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":2174},"type":"message"}],"speed":"standard"},"diagnostics":null},"requestId":"req_011CbXzbhtKfKqxAcvndHEqz","attributionMcpServer":"ccd_session","attributionMcpTool":"mark_chapter","type":"assistant","uuid":"1f2550be-4ccb-485f-b144-9558db7714e8","timestamp":"2026-05-30T02:50:48.568Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"claude-desktop","cwd":"/Users/scottdensmore/Developer/scottdensmore/movieswiftui/MovieSwift","sessionId":"2cae28a4-28e8-4bfa-9225-7682543f3664","version":"2.1.149","gitBranch":"modernize/parameterize-people-actions-tests","slug":"snuggly-shimmying-pebble"}
{"parentUuid":"1f2550be-4ccb-485f-b144-9558db7714e8","isSidechain":false,"message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-7","id":"msg_01Wt2w9QA2j6asbW8ASYgVSc","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01JAeMD1LAs69J5wvYYJSPhG","name":"Bash","input":{"command":"git -C /Users/scottdensmore/Developer/scottdensmore/movieswiftui add MovieSwift/MovieSwiftTests/PeopleActionsTests.swift && git -C /Users/scottdensmore/Developer/scottdensmore/movieswiftui commit -m \"$(cat <<'EOF'\ntest(people-actions): parameterize 5 DoesNotDispatchOnFailure tests with @Test(arguments:)\n\nCollapses the 5 nearly-identical `fetchXDoesNotDispatchOnFailure` tests\ninto one parameterized test\n`fetchActionDoesNotDispatchDataActionOnFailure(kind:)` that iterates\nover a `FailureFetchKind` enum (FetchDetail, FetchImages,\nFetchPeopleCredits, FetchMovieCasts, FetchSearch). The dispatch\nindirection goes through an instance-method switch rather than a\nstruct of `@Sendable` closures so `DispatchFunction` (a non-Sendable\nfunction type) doesn't have to cross the `@Test(arguments:)` boundary.\n\nThe success-side tests stay individual: each one verifies action-\nspecific fields (FetchDetail asserts person.id/name, FetchMovieCasts\nasserts response.cast/crew names + URL path, etc.) and forcing them\ninto a single signature would obscure intent. FetchPopular's pair\nalso stays as-is — its failure path dispatches `PopularRequestFailed`\nrather than just \"not dispatching SetX\", so it doesn't fit the\nshared shape.\n\n`@Test` method is declared `private` because its parameter type\n`FailureFetchKind` is private (Swift Testing macros do work on\nprivate methods).\n\nNet: PeopleActionsTests goes from 12 tests to 8 tests (5 success +\n1 parameterized failure covering 5 cases + 2 FetchPopular). All\ngreen locally.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.7 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>\nEOF\n)\"","description":"Commit PeopleActionsTests parameterization"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":2174,"cache_read_input_tokens":196800,"output_tokens":872,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":2174,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[{"input_tokens":1,"output_tokens":872,"cache_read_input_tokens":196800,"cache_creation_input_tokens":2174,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":2174},"type":"message"}],"speed":"standard"},"diagnostics":null},"requestId":"req_011CbXzbhtKfKqxAcvndHEqz","attributionMcpServer":"ccd_session","attributionMcpTool":"mark_chapter","type":"assistant","uuid":"08aa3b67-849d-4159-b71d-6bc69c2af111","timestamp":"2026-05-30T02:50:57.234Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"claude-desktop","cwd":"/Users/scottdensmore/Developer/scottdensmore/movieswiftui/MovieSwift","sessionId":"2cae28a4-28e8-4bfa-9225-7682543f3664","version":"2.1.149","gitBranch":"modernize/parameterize-people-actions-tests","slug":"snuggly-shimmying-pebble"}
